Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.51,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:246142,247518}You little…!{NOTE:お前な～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.52,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:248311,249520}By the way, Lute.{NOTE:そうだ、リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.64,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:249520,250646}Hm?{NOTE:んっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:15.06,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:250646,255067}How about we split up in our search for Avinia tomorrow?{NOTE:あしたは別々のルートでアユリアを捜すっていうのはどうかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.02,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:255067,256027}Okay.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.69,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:256027,259697}I guess I see how splitting up might be useful.{NOTE:確かに別々の道を行くのはいいかもな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:20.61,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:259697,260615}All right.{NOTE:よし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.45,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:260615,262450}Then let's do so first thing tomorrow.{NOTE:夜が明けたらそうしよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.70,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:262450,263701}Okay.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.32,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:263701,266329}There are some things\Nwe'd like to check out for ourselves.{NOTE:俺たちは色々気になることもあるし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.62,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:266329,268623}So we'll go to Trese Desert.{NOTE:クバ砂漠の方に行ってみるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.45,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:268623,270458}What about us, then?{NOTE:じゃあ俺たちはどうする？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.95,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:270458,271959}Hmm…{NOTE:う～ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.29,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:274462,276297}Hey, be serious about this.{NOTE:真面目に考えろよな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.50,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:277173,279509}It got out {\i1}because{\i0} I was serious.{NOTE:考えてるから出ちゃったんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:279509,281552}Are you kidding me…?{NOTE:何だよそれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.67,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:281552,283679}I focused really hard and then… just… you know.{NOTE:力が入っちゃったんだつい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.05,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:285348,287058}I told you to knock it off.{NOTE:だからやめろって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.26,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:287058,290269}And I told you that it goes out when I focus!{NOTE:だから力が入っちゃうと出ちゃうんだって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.97,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:290269,291979}Let's all stay calm, shall we?{NOTE:まあまあお二人とも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:53.98,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:292688,293981}I know.{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:58.48,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:293981,298486}How about you guys talk to some Felynes?{NOTE:リュートとナビルーはアイルーたちに話を聞きに行ったらどうかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.07,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:298486,300071}At Pawpad Place?{NOTE:ニクキュー村へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.03,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:300071,301030}Yup.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.57,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:301030,304575}Felynes might know some important information.{NOTE:アイルーたちから何か聞けるかもしれないし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.53,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:304575,306536}That's a good idea!{NOTE:それはいい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:09.33,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:306536,309330}They have quite the Felyne Network over there.{NOTE:あそこにはアイルーネットワークがあるし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:13.25,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:309330,313251}And also Navirou is exalted as a god in there.{NOTE:何たってナビルーは神としてあがめられているしな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.66,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:313251,314669}Are you, now?{NOTE:そうなのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.12,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:314669,316128}Have you forgotten?{NOTE:忘れたのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.46,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:316128,318464}That warm reception last time we went there.{NOTE:前に行ったときのあの歓迎ぶりを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.38,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:318965,320383}Hmm…{NOTE:う～ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.30,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:321175,322301}Oh well.{NOTE:まあいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:24.80,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:322301,324804}Anyway, we'll go to the Pawpad Place.{NOTE:ナビルーたちはニクキュー村に行くとしよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.80,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:325680,326806}I like it.{NOTE:それがいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.43,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:326806,328432}Good night.{NOTE:じゃあおやすみ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.93,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:333479,334939}He's fallen asleep.{NOTE:寝ちゃいましたよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.73,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:335773,336732}That was quick!{NOTE:早っ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:339527,340945}How can he even sleep like that?{NOTE:寝てもかよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.45,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:346200,349453}We'll definitely find Avinia.{NOTE:絶対に見つけようなアユリアを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.45,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:349453,350454}Yeah.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.87,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:354792,357879}I hope Cheval and Cryo don't get lost.{NOTE:シュヴァルたち、迷ったりしてないよな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:03.09,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:359005,363092}You should worry about yourself before them.{NOTE:その前に自分たちの心配をすべきだと思うが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.34,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:363092,365344}Why? Navigation is your responsibility, right?{NOTE:ナビはナビルーの役目だろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.63,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:365344,366637}Well…{NOTE:う～ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.43,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:368598,371434}Be serious.{NOTE:真面目に考えろよな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:14.06,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:371434,374061}How do we get to Pawpad Place?{NOTE:どっちへ行けばニクキュー村か。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:17.94,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:374061,377940}It's because I'm serious that I fart.{NOTE:真面目に考えてるから力が入っておならが出るんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.73,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:377940,379734}That again…?{NOTE:何だよそれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.69,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:379734,382695}It's not like I fart because I like it.{NOTE:ナビルーだって好きでおならしてるわけじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.53,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:383779,387533}So which way is Pawpad Place?{NOTE:で、どっちだ？ニクキュー村は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.78,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:387533,388784}Let's see…{NOTE:そうだな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.66,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:389452,390661}Hmm.{NOTE:う～ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.33,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:393664,396334}Don't answer me with a fart!{NOTE:だからおならで答えるなって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.33,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:396334,399337}I told you, I focus – I fart!\NWhat part of it you don't understand?{NOTE:だから真面目に考えてるから出ちゃうんだって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:41.42,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:400838,401422}What was that!?{NOTE:何だ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.05,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:403215,404050}A monster!?{NOTE:モンスターか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.40,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:422485,425404}You're… Dr. Manelger's assistant, right?{NOTE:お前マネルガーの助手だよな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.28,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:425404,426280}Yeah!{NOTE:そうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.28,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:426280,427281}You're Itsy-Bits!{NOTE:イチビッツだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.49,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:428282,431494}Well, well! Good timing.{NOTE:これはこれは。いいところで会えました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.57,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:431494,433579}Really, good timing!{NOTE:ホントにいいところで会えました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:16.62,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:434455,436624}It's so important, I said it twice.{NOTE:大事なことなので二度言いました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:21.25,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:437291,441253}Well the last thing we wanted to do was bump into you. Right?{NOTE:別に俺たちは全然会いたいと思ってなかったよな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.17,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:441253,442171}Right.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.79,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:442171,443798}What he said.{NOTE:まったくだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:27.63,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:443798,447635}Please don't be so stiff and save Doctor.{NOTE:そう言わず博士を助けてくださいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:447635,448552}Eh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.72,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:448552,450721}What's wrong with Manelger?{NOTE:マネルガーがどうかしたのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.01,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:450721,453015}He's acting strange.{NOTE:どうも様子がおかしいんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.10,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:453015,455101}Anyway, please come with me.{NOTE:とにかく一緒に来てください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:39.39,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:455977,459397}Sorry, but Navirou's pretty busy right now.{NOTE:悪いがナビルーたちは今忙しいんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.35,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:459397,462358}We're looking for the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズを捜してるんでな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.31,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:462358,464318}And that's why we must refuse.{NOTE:というわけで断る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:46.69,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:464318,466696}Don't be so stiff and please come with me.{NOTE:そう言わず来てくださいって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.15,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:466696,468155}Ah, I forgot!{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.61,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:468155,470616}Dr. Manelger is a well-informed person…{NOTE:物知りマネルガー博士のことですから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:55.78,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:470616,475788}…there's no mistake he has picked up information about the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:…ちまたで噂のﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞとやらのことも知ってるに違いありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:58.45,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:475788,478457}He might've researched them by accident, you see.{NOTE:何かチラッと調べてましたから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.33,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:478457,480334}Really…?{NOTE:ホントか～？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:04.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:480334,484839}I wouldn't expect much,\Nbut maybe we should check this out…?{NOTE:あんまり当てにならないけど一応行ってみるか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.71,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:484839,487717}We might pick up some clues.{NOTE:何か情報が得られるかもしれないし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.88,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:487717,490886}And if they don't have anything,\Nwe'll just hit the road to Pawpad Place.{NOTE:何もなければとっととニクキュー村を目指せばいいし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:19.10,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:493931,499103}"The genius doctor is no more…"{NOTE:｢天才博士はもういない｣}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.68,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:499103,501689}"It was so fleeting."{NOTE:｢はかなかった｣}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.85,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:501689,503858}"It was so fleeting…"{NOTE:｢はかなかった｣}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:504567,505943}What… is he doing?{NOTE:何してるんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.36,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:505943,507361}Is he a kid or what?{NOTE:子供か！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.86,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:507361,510865}See, ever since the incident with the Black Blight…{NOTE:ですから博士は黒の凶気の事件以来…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:35.36,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:510865,515369}…Doctor has lost his motivation to study and became a shadow of his former self.{NOTE:…研究する意欲を失って抜け殻になってしまったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.12,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:515369,517121}Isn't that for the better?{NOTE:いいことじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.95,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:517121,519957}This is far better than his mischief.{NOTE:また悪さをするよりずっとましだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:40.87,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:519957,520875}Yup.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.20,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:520875,522209}Fully agreed.{NOTE:言えてるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.33,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:522209,525337}But he's not this kind of doctor!{NOTE:でもそんなの博士じゃありません！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.75,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:525337,528758}He's a scientist immersed in research.{NOTE:博士は研究に没頭してこそ博士なのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:52.01,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:528758,532011}Please, put some life back to him.{NOTE:どうかお二人で活を入れてやってください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.76,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:532011,533763}Hmm…{NOTE:う～ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:56.72,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:533763,536724}I guess we can accept if you can give us donuts.{NOTE:ドーナツくれたら引き受けてもいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:57.30,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:536724,537308}Ah!{NOTE:あっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.22,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:537308,541228}There are some donuts-like things in the laboratory.{NOTE:ドーナツ的な物なら研究所にありますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.85,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:541228,542855}Really!?{NOTE:ホントか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:542855,546857}Let's try asking him about the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:まあ聞いてみるか。ブラックライダーズのこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.44,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:546857,548444}Hey! Manelger!{NOTE:おいマネルガー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.40,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:550321,551405}He~y!{NOTE:お～い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.57,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:553199,554575}It's useless.{NOTE:駄目だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.41,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:554575,556410}He doesn't react at all.{NOTE:全然反応しない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:17.62,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:556410,557620}That's right.{NOTE:そうなんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.28,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:557620,559288}He's been like this all this time.{NOTE:ずっとあの調子で…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:23.70,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:559288,563709}Then that means we can't ask him anything about the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:じゃあきっと何にも聞けないな。ブラックライダーズのこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.12,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:563709,565127}Let's head back, Navirou.{NOTE:引き返そうナビルー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.38,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:568506,569381}Hmm!?{NOTE:んっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.05,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:570841,573052}What was that special fart!?{NOTE:何だその特殊なおならは！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.22,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:573719,574220}Oh?{NOTE:おっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.43,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:576514,578432}Did you notice it?{NOTE:気付いちゃったか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.93,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:578432,581936}My, my! If it isn't Lute and Navirou!{NOTE:これはこれはリュート君たちではないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.23,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:581936,584230}So? What was that fart?{NOTE:で今のおならはいったい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:47.27,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:584230,587274}A normal fart would never smell like that.{NOTE:このにおいただのおならでは決してない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.69,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:587274,588692}Oh!{NOTE:お～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.07,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:588692,591070}Doctor has spoken for the first time in a long while!{NOTE:博士が久々にしゃべりました！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.44,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:594031,595449}I see.{NOTE:なるほど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:10:01.49,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:595449,601497}So the Rite of Channeling has granted you a new kind of far— I mean, power?{NOTE:それは伝承の儀により得た新たなおなら…あっいや。力というわけか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.04,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:601497,603040}That's how it is.{NOTE:そういうことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.25,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:603040,605251}It's a pretty troublesome power, though.{NOTE:迷惑な力だけどな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:08.46,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:605251,608462}So how did you exactly acquire it?{NOTE:で、それはどうやって手に入れるのだね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:12.04,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:608462,612049}If you tell me everything you know\Nabout the Ebon Riders…{NOTE:お前が知ってるﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞのことを教えてくれたら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.46,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:612049,614468}…I'll talk to you about the Rite of Channeling.{NOTE:…伝承の儀のことを話してやる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.30,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:614468,617304}Do we have any data on the Ebon Riders?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズとは例のあれか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.72,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:617304,618722}Yes.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:22.05,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:618722,622059}It's a group rumored to hunt for Kinship Stones in various places.{NOTE:各地で絆石狩りをしてるって噂のやつらです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.02,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:623144,625020}Who are they?{NOTE:やつらは何者なんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.18,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:625020,626188}Where are they?{NOTE:どこにいる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.31,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:626188,628315}I-I don't know the details.{NOTE:く…詳しくは知りません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:31.86,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:628315,631861}Only that there's a group like that…{NOTE:ただそういう連中がいるってことぐらいしか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.86,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:631861,633863}Right. We don't know.{NOTE:そうだ。よくは知らん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:37.32,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:633863,637324}But I think I've researched their whereabouts before.{NOTE:何となくやつらの居場所は調べてみたが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.95,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:637324,638951}You did?{NOTE:調べたのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.82,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:638951,640828}So where are they?{NOTE:で、どこなんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:44.99,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:640828,644999}Hmm… I lost interest with them so I made a note.{NOTE:う～ん、興味ないのでその辺にメモを残しておいたはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:48.96,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:644999,648961}Didn't you draw a map of their hideout or something?{NOTE:地図とか描いてませんでしたっけ？彼らのアジトの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:53.34,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:648961,653340}Did I draw it…? Did I not?{NOTE:調べて描いたような描いてないような…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.30,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:653340,654300}Ah…{NOTE:あ～…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.55,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:654300,655551}I forgot.{NOTE:忘れたなもうな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:11:02.05,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:656510,662057}There you have it. He's lost his motivation for everything.{NOTE:…とまあこんな具合で何事にもやる気を失ってる状態なんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.64,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:662057,663642}It's useless.{NOTE:駄目だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.47,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:663642,666478}We won't get any info from him.{NOTE:ﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞのこと聞き出せそうもない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.23,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:666478,668230}Yeah.{NOTE:だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.69,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:668230,669690}Now that we know for sure…{NOTE:そうと分かれば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.02,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:669690,671025}…we're leaving.{NOTE:帰るか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.35,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:671025,672359}Exactly.{NOTE:そうしよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.06,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:672359,674069}Hey!{NOTE:ってちょっと～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.03,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:674069,676030}What about the poor Doctor?{NOTE:博士はどうするんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:18.24,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:676030,678240}Are you going to forsake us?{NOTE:見捨てるつもりですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:21.82,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:678240,681827}Sorry, but we can't do anything.{NOTE:悪いけど俺たち今それどころじゃないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.82,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:681827,683829}We're looking for our friend.{NOTE:大事な仲間を捜してる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.37,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:683829,685372}That's just how it is.{NOTE:そういうことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.41,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:685372,687416}So see ya.{NOTE:ってわけでじゃあな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.08,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:687416,689084}I know! Donuts!{NOTE:そうだドーナツ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.08,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:689084,691086}Didn't you want a donut?{NOTE:ドーナツはいらないんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.08,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:691086,693088}Ah! I did!{NOTE:あ～！それはいる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.38,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:693088,695382}And we did come all the way here, after all.{NOTE:わざわざ寄ってやったんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.88,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:695382,696884}Hand over the donuts.{NOTE:ドーナツよこせ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.05,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:696884,698052}There they are.{NOTE:ほらそこに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:39.47,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:698844,699470}Oh!{NOTE:おっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:42.47,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:700471,702473}I'll help myself to it!{NOTE:それは頂いていくぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:45.64,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:702473,705643}Without doing anything about the Doctor?{NOTE:博士に何もしてくれてないのにですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.64,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:705643,707645}You brought us here to examine him.{NOTE:様子を見に来てやった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.43,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:707645,709438}He'll be fine.{NOTE:大丈夫だそいつは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.14,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:709438,711148}Seems so.{NOTE:まあそうだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:54.69,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:711148,714693}Besides, it's better for the world if he stays docile.{NOTE:おとなしくしてもらった方が世の中のためでもあるしな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.02,Default,Itsy-Bits,0,0,0,,{TIME:715903,717029}I can't believe it…{NOTE:そんな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.32,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:717905,719323}Here comes my reward.{NOTE:ではいただき！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:01.99,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:721116,721992}Ah!{NOTE:あ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.03,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:721992,723035}That's…!{NOTE:それは！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:03.82,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:723035,723827}Ah?{NOTE:あっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:06.16,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:723827,726163}That's no ordinary donut!{NOTE:ドーナツであってドーナツでない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.54,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:726163,728540}It's a donutshroom.{NOTE:ドーナツ茸というものだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.79,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:728540,729792}Donutshroom?{NOTE:ドーナツ茸？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:13.21,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:732586,733212}What!?{NOTE:なっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.13,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:735798,737132}What in the world…!?{NOTE:何だこれは!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.51,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:737883,740511}To put it simply, it's a poisonous mushroom.{NOTE:簡単に言うと毒キノコだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.88,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:740511,741887}Eh!?{NOTE:え～!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:741887,743555}Poisonous mushroom!?{NOTE:毒キノコ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.80,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:743555,745808}I-Is Na-Na-Navirou going to die!?{NOTE:ナ、ナ、ナ、ナビルーは死ぬのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.39,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:745808,747393}Am I going to die!?{NOTE:死んじゃうのか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.31,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:747393,750312}Doctor! Do something, please!{NOTE:博士！何とかしてくれよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:31.64,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:750312,751647}Don't worry.{NOTE:安心しろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.64,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:751647,753649}It's not life-threatening.{NOTE:命に別条はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:753649,755859}Oh, well that's a relief.{NOTE:何だ…そうなんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.02,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:755859,758028}Don't scare me like that.{NOTE:脅かすなよ～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:38.98,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:758028,758988}However!{NOTE:だが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:41.99,Default,Manelger,0,0,0,,{TIME:759863,761991}It makes you fart on a grand scale.{NOTE:盛大におならが出る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.21,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:774378,776213}What a waste of time.{NOTE:とんだ時間の無駄だったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.09,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:777131,778090}More importantly…{NOTE:っていうか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:58.59,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:778090,778590}Huh?{NOTE:んっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.34,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:780092,782344}What should I do about my tummy?{NOTE:このおなかどうすれば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.22,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:783262,785222}You've got no choice but to fart it out.{NOTE:おならを出しきるしかないだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.68,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:786056,787683}Manelger said so himself.{NOTE:マネルガーもそう言ってたし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.56,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:790185,792563}Don't come any closer.{NOTE:絶対それ以上近づくなよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:17.48,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:793856,797484}But this might be actually useful a bit!{NOTE:でもこれちょっと使えるかもしれないぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.61,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:797484,799611}With the destructive power of this smell…{NOTE:このにおいの破壊力で…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:23.07,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:799611,803073}…we might defeat the Ebon Riders!{NOTE:…ブラックライダーズのやつらを倒せるかもしれん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.70,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:803073,804700}You're right.{NOTE:そうだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.24,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:804700,807244}But don't come anywhere near me.{NOTE:でも俺には近づくなよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.24,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:807244,808245}So?{NOTE:で？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.87,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:808245,809872}Which way is Pawpad Place?{NOTE:ニクキュー村はどっちだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.29,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:811040,812291}That way.{NOTE:あっちだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.58,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:812291,814585}So this way, huh?{NOTE:じゃあこっちだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:38.00,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:814585,818005}– And keep that smell away from me.\N– Nya-ow!{NOTE:—におうから離れてついてこいよ。\\N—ニャグゥ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.43,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:824887,827431}Hey! Long time no see, everyone!{NOTE:お～！久しぶり～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.85,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:827431,829850}It's Master Navirou!{NOTE:ナビルーさまだぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:50.55,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,{TIME:829850,830559}Eh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.39,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,{TIME:831393,832394}Eh!?{NOTE:え～!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.27,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:833354,834271}What's wrong?{NOTE:どうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.44,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:837900,839443}What's with him?{NOTE:どうしたんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:04.32,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:839443,844323}After they were all like\N"welcome, Master Rider" last time…{NOTE:前はライダーさまとオトモアイルーとかいって歓迎してくれたのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:09.78,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:844323,849787}Our sudden comeback must have been too much amazement and fear at once so he escaped.{NOTE:突然出てきたから、驚きと恐怖のあまりおののいて逃げ出したに違いない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.24,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:849787,851246}I wonder about that…{NOTE:そうか～？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.83,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,{TIME:851246,852831}Navirou came back-nyaa!{NOTE:ナビルーが来たニャー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.50,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,{TIME:855042,856502}Navirou!{NOTE:ナビルー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.66,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,{TIME:856502,857669}Navirou!{NOTE:ナビルー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.83,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:857669,858837}See?{NOTE:ほら見ろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.92,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:858837,860923}It's just like Navirou told you!{NOTE:ナビルーの言ったとおりだ！}
